{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Node.previousSibling","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/previousSibling","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/baseURI\"><code>baseURI</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/childNodes\"><code>childNodes</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/firstChild\"><code>firstChild</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isConnected\"><code>isConnected</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/lastChild\"><code>lastChild</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/nextSibling\"><code>nextSibling</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeName\"><code>nodeName</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeType\"><code>nodeType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeValue\"><code>nodeValue</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/ownerDocument\"><code>ownerDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/parentElement\"><code>parentElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/parentNode\"><code>parentNode</code></a></li><li><em><code>previousSibling</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/textContent\"><code>textContent</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/appendChild\"><code>appendChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/cloneNode\"><code>cloneNode()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/compareDocumentPosition\"><code>compareDocumentPosition()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/contains\"><code>contains()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/getRootNode\"><code>getRootNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/hasChildNodes\"><code>hasChildNodes()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/insertBefore\"><code>insertBefore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isDefaultNamespace\"><code>isDefaultNamespace()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isEqualNode\"><code>isEqualNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isSameNode\"><code>isSameNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isSupported\"><code>isSupported()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupNamespaceURI\"><code>lookupNamespaceURI()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupPrefix\"><code>lookupPrefix()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/normalize\"><code>normalize()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/removeChild\"><code>removeChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/replaceChild\"><code>replaceChild()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n<p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Allgemein","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Gibt den Datenknoten zurück, der entsprechend der childNodes-Liste des Elternelements dem gegebenen Datenknoten direkt vorangestellt ist. Falls der übergebene Knoten bereits der erste in dieser Liste ist, wird null zurückgegeben.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">vorangestellterKnoten = node.previousSibling;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Beispiele","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Folgendes HTML-Dokument ist gegeben:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Das ist eine DIV-Box<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Hier steht Text!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Punkt 1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Punkt 2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>So kann der vorangestellte Datenknoten von <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code> ermittelt werden:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:javascript notranslate\"><code>\t<span class=\"token comment\">// Diese Variable speichert eine Referenz auf das letzte Element, das &lt;body&gt; enthält, also &lt;ul&gt;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> element <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>body<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>children<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">// Nun ermitteln wir durch previousSibling den vorangestellten Knoten</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> vorangestellterKnoten <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> element<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>previousSibling<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">// Ausgabe des Knoten-Namens</span>\n\t<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>vorangestellterKnoten<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nodeName<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>Erläuterung:</strong></p>\n<p>Die Variable <code><var>element</var></code> enthält das letzte Kindelement des -Tags, also <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code>. <code><var>vorangestellterKnoten</var></code> speichert den direkt vorangestellten Geschwisterknoten von <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code>. In diesem Fall ist das ein Textknoten der einen Zeilenvorschub und vier Leerzeichen enthält, die sich in dem HTML-Dokument zwischen dem <code>&gt;</code> von <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> und dem <code>&lt;</code> des <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code> befinden. Das alert()-Fenster gibt somit <code>#text</code> aus.</p>\n<p>So können alle vorangestellten Datenknoten eines Elements ermittelt werden:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:javascript notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> element <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>body<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>children<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> liste <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">while</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>element<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>previousSibling<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> element <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> liste<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>liste<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>element<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>previousSibling<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Das Skript erzeugt ein Array <code><var>liste</var></code> mit folgendem Inhalt:</p>\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">Array[5]\n  0: Text\n  1: HTMLParagraphElement\n  2: Text\n  3: HTMLDivElement\n  4: Text\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Anmerkungen","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Um statt dem vorangestellten Datenknoten den Nächsten zu erhalten, verwenden Sie <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/nextSibling\"><code>Node.nextSibling</code></a>.<br>\n Da die Eigenschaft <code>previousSibling</code> Textknoten berücksichtigt, kann es sein, dass Sie statt des vorangestellten Elements einen Textknoten als Rückgabewert erhalten. Oft passiert das durch Whitespace aller Art (z.B. Leerzeichen, Zeilenvorschübe), der sich zwischen den beiden Elementen befindet und von <code>previousSibling</code> als Textknoten interpretiert wird.<br>\n Falls Textknoten nicht berücksichtigt werden sollen, verwenden Sie stattdessen <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/previousElementSibling\"><code>Element.previousElementSibling</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/REC-DOM-Level-1/level-one-core.html#attribute-previousSibling\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 1 Core: previousSibling</a>&nbsp;(en)</li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-640FB3C8\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 Core: previousSibling</a>&nbsp;(en)</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/nextSibling\"><code>Node.nextSibling</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/previousElementSibling\"><code>Element.previousElementSibling</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/childNodes\"><code>Node.childNodes</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Gibt den Datenknoten zurück, der entsprechend der childNodes-Liste des Elternelements dem gegebenen Datenknoten direkt vorangestellt ist. Falls der übergebene Knoten bereits der erste in dieser Liste ist, wird null zurückgegeben.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.previousSibling","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Node.previousSibling","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.previousSibling","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.previousSibling","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Node.previousSibling","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"element.previousSibling","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Node.previousSibling","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Node.previousSibling","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.previousSibling","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/node/previoussibling","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/node/previoussibling/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node","title":"Node"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/previousSibling","title":"Node.previousSibling"}],"pageTitle":"Node.previousSibling - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}